title: Windows 7 x86 Service Pack 1 - ALL VERSIONS
description:
This is an ISO of Windows 7 Service Pack 1 (SP1). This version of the ISO has been modified with the ei.cfg removal tool, so it can install ALL the versions of Windows 7 SP1 x86.

This ISO was downloaded from Microsoft's official servers, then one file was removed to permit version installation. There is NO spyware, NO malware, and NO viruses on this ISO. The image is not preactivated, you will need to supply a product key
